==English==
===Noun===
'''[[cardinal]] [[symptom]]'''
#{{medicine}} the [[primary]] or [[major]] symptom by which a [[diagnosis]] is made
#(''homeopathy'') the particular symptom which is regarded most important for choosing the curing substance

